{"tid":925801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【命運安排】登記捐骨髓只為識女仔 結果救返病童仲娶得美人歸","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T13:31:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"99dd589ce2539baf6ef3feadbdba1d816b779369","tid":925801,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"「我不太相信因果報應，但最終大家都有個愉快結局，實在太好了。」英國一名29歲男子得知心儀女同事登記當骨髓捐贈者後，為討佳人歡心決定一同登記，沒想到他的骨髓與一名病童脗合，男童接受移植後痊癒，男子亦娶得美人歸。<br />\n在投資銀行三菱日聯（MUFG）工作的希金斯（Billy Higgins），7年前暗戀女同事威利斯（Kate Willis），決定與對方一同參與骨髓捐贈者招募活動，「我們之前聊過天，我當時覺得是深入認識她的好機會，也在想如果加入活動，定可在她心中留下好印象。」<br />\n希金斯的這一步不單為自己「加分」，更拯救了現年10歲的男童克羅斯（Rupert Cross）。克羅斯2014年不時頭痛求醫，2年後確診患上骨髓生成不良綜合症（myelodysplastic syndrome），這病會令骨髓製造不成熟細胞而非紅血球，有機會轉化成白血病，或令免疫系統惡化進而危及生命。<br />\n克羅斯家人與他的骨髓並不脗合無法捐贈，不過希金斯就是合適的捐贈者，並在2016年6月完成移植手術。2年過去，克羅斯現已痊癒並可上學，「我覺得很幸運......，不相信有人會捐骨髓給我」。<br />\n希金斯上月與克羅斯一家見面，並向對方轉達另一個喜訊－－他與威利斯結婚了。克羅斯母親十分感謝希金斯，「這是個奇妙的故事，他（希金斯）參加只因他喜歡的女孩也在那裡，要不是威利斯，這一切都不會發生。現在他們結婚了......，這故事很瘋狂。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543650458_4148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543650458_4148.jpg&h=c4c20cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181203/58979951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F58979951&d=JdofEqXGygwe9bBNhTug2gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=dbd66291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F58979951&h=db336495\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181203/58979951</a>"},{"pid":"a458c82b5eaf8ad273bedb4fd7718a49e97651f1","tid":925801,"uid":17866,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔個ibanker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f88e8a99adb7f9bb0eaa1934068ae379a0e5f8","tid":925801,"uid":66822,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"如果捐骨髓就溝到女 咁我都捐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e863c88129f68f30c8f5a835906891a96a853a","tid":925801,"uid":35430,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"c2f88e8a99adb7f9bb0eaa1934068ae379a0e5f8","tid":925801,"uid":66822,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"如果捐骨髓就溝到女 咁我都捐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"冇人要你d骨髓<br />\n骨髓有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f81be6115e5ed5f63a38b0c74cbe4824b32094","tid":925801,"uid":198251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2f88e8a99adb7f9bb0eaa1934068ae379a0e5f8","tid":925801,"uid":66822,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"如果捐骨髓就溝到女 咁我都捐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:16:10.000Z","msg":"都係去泰國捐精吧啦 可能仲易D溝到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b471511c1e186bc1f0344cf8929f9c4c79d4934","tid":925801,"uid":187955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"係咪招聘廣告黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e091be8a756beb8a4f3d3457dc60fb51605de1","tid":925801,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33f52049f5b9286c01bc432f0d6ef805ab523e8","tid":925801,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:20:17.000Z","